<subSubSection pageId="18" pageNumber="283" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="18.[160,1156,319,553]" box="[160,262,319,345]" pageId="18" pageNumber="283">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[160,262,319,345]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="283">Remarks</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="18.[160,1156,319,553]" pageId="18" pageNumber="283">
According to Lamarck’s description (1816) and his illustrations, our specimens resemble 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Lamarck" authorityYear="1816" box="[204,348,389,414]" class="Gastropoda" family="Phylliroidae" genus="Phylliroe" kingdom="Animalia" order="Nudibranchia" pageId="18" pageNumber="283" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="bucephala">
<emphasis box="[204,348,389,414]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="283">P. bucephala</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, but a molecular analysis is required to validate its identity due to its similarities to 
<taxonomicName authority="Eschscholtz, 1825" authorityName="Eschscholtz" authorityYear="1825" box="[326,710,424,449]" class="Gastropoda" family="Phylliroidae" genus="Phylliroe" kingdom="Animalia" order="Nudibranchia" pageId="18" pageNumber="283" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="lichtensteinii">
<emphasis box="[326,494,424,449]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="283">P. lichtensteinii</emphasis>
Eschscholtz, 1825
</taxonomicName>
, which has also been recorded in the Mediterranean Sea. In any case, this represents the first record of the genus 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Peron and Lesueur" authorityYear="1810" box="[1061,1155,459,484]" class="Gastropoda" family="Phylliroidae" genus="Phylliroe" kingdom="Animalia" order="Nudibranchia" pageId="18" pageNumber="283" phylum="Mollusca" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1061,1155,459,484]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="283">Phylliroe</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
on the Iberian Spanish coast.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="18.[160,1156,319,553]" box="[405,826,528,553]" pageId="18" pageNumber="283">
Family 
<taxonomicName authority="Odhner, 1934" authorityName="Odhner" authorityYear="1934" box="[486,826,528,553]" class="Gastropoda" family="Eubranchidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Nudibranchia" pageId="18" pageNumber="283" phylum="Mollusca" rank="family">EUBRANCHIDAE Odhner, 1934</taxonomicName>
</paragraph>
